name: DiffLoRA_FaceShadowTweaker
description:
This LoRA is a LoRA that arbitrarily switches the shadows and highlights of the face. It was created by a technique called “コピー機LoRA” in Japanese. By using LoRA with intentional overfitting and extracting differences in the model, changes are made only to specific points. I couldn’t think of an appropriate English translation, so I tentatively abbreviated it to “difference LoRA”.DiffLoRA.

Thank you

  • https://huggingface.co/2vXpSwA7/iroiro-lora

  • Anon!

More detailed: My trash blog - > https://1lemon1lemon.netlify.app/2023-06-27_difflora/
